# ============================================================
# SKILL CORE RUNTIME
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: skill
scope: skill.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for skill.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers skill visibility,
proficiency-aware display,
applicability-aware display,
historical skill reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- skill identity must resolve
- holder basis must resolve
- proficiency/applicability scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid skill identity
- invalid holder basis
- invalid applicability scope
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish skill state,
proficiency display,
applicability display,
historical reference,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- skill runtime scope is explicit
- applicability-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
